{"tid":1771391,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"淺入股票投資：估值現金流點計？","createTime":"2019-12-06T00:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T17:45:21.000Z","uid":112161,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de6fc29e86b5255d49d422aab7526e9f38809735","tid":1771391,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:06:17.000Z","msg":"【淺入股票投資：估值現金流點計？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/1001058226944476?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F567419136975056%2Fposts%2F1001058226944476%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=6e083fb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/567419136975056/posts/1001058226944476?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n上幾篇提到估值時的折現率如何推算，今次就開始略講估值時的「現金流」到底係乜？<br />\n<br />\n公司透過銷售可以賺到收入（Revenue），但收入仍未可以袋入股東袋中，因為銷售是有成本的。例如生果檔賣生果，亦要入貨訂生果。除了生果的來貨成本，生果檔更要支付果攤的「燈油火蠟」，最後更要交稅，餘下的才是果檔老闆賺到的錢。之不過，果檔老闆所賺到的錢，卻又未必等於老闆在期內所得的淨現金流入。<br />\n<br />\n原因是，一檔生意的營運通常會涉及很多「非現金交易」。這些「非現金交易」同樣會影響到盈利的數值，若折現時未有考慮清楚，所得的估值就有可能存在重大偏差。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是「非現金交易」呢？顧名思義就是，不會構成實際現金流出或流入的項目，但項目數值對於會計帳目卻有著實質影響。<br />\n<br />\n以生果檔為例，果檔或會接受一些價值較大的商業訂單，而由於訂單貨值大，客戶未必會即時以現金支付，更可能會在收貨後才繳清帳單（亦可視為賒售或Credit Sales）。這就構成了生果檔的「應收款項（Accounts Receivable）」，即生果檔應該在未來收取的款項。<br />\n<br />\n這項交易之中，生果檔在交貨後就已完成了銷售，但客戶卻只承諾會在指定期內「找數」。帳面上，由於銷售已完成，生果檔仍要在會計帳目中納入這單生意的收入與相應開支；但生果檔在客戶「找數」前卻沒有得到任何現金流入。<br />\n<br />\n除了賒售之外，常見的「非現金交易」仍有很多，下篇繼續！"},{"pid":"b9ca7b3b2697ae00944fb5b550cafe0e3831b779","tid":1771391,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"難Ching<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83e56c1e5f50a59b772ce5c8020af259df98857a","tid":1771391,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9ca7b3b2697ae00944fb5b550cafe0e3831b779","tid":1771391,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T02:16:12.000Z","msg":"難Ching<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e982297fb0624ba9919b622142605dfe307c1c","tid":1771391,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已經被入侵!!!星期六行動post冇人推，大家入黎同我推爆佢春袋!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hksuckagain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhksuckagain&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=27910c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hksuckagain</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【緊急!!!連登冇人推行動post!!!】和理非12.7一齊遊車河塞春袋!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a41959a8146221d5df824dabca9b61704e71452e","tid":1771391,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e982297fb0624ba9919b622142605dfe307c1c","tid":1771391,"uid":92247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登已經被入侵!!!星期六行動post冇人推，大家入黎同我推爆佢春袋!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/hksuckagain\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhksuckagain&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=27910c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hksuckagain</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【緊急!!!連登冇人推行動post!!!】和理非12.7一齊遊車河塞春袋!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1771177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1771177</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"r